<div class="row" style="margin:0px;">
    <div class="col-lg-12" style="background-color:rgb(212, 250, 214); padding:20px; display:inline-block; width:100%; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);">
        <p style="font-size: 30px; text-align:center; font-family: Arial; font-weight:bold;">WHAT WE DO</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px; text-align:justify; font-family: Arial; font-weight:bold;">Save A Pet Florida, Inc. was originally founded as “Save Precious Lives, Inc.” by Gertrude Maxwell in 1978.  The name was changed to Save A Pet Florida, Inc. on January 19, 1988. Every day our volunteers donate their time to rescue homeless animals from a parking lot, a car engine, an abandoned building, etc.</p>
